      "yeas": "Mayor Katz, Councillor Browaty, Councillor Eadie, Councillor Fielding, Councillor Gerbasi, Councillor Havixbeck, Councillor Mayes, Councillor Nordman, Councillor Pagtakhan, Councillor Smith, Councillor Steen, Councillor Vandal, Councillor Wyatt, Councillor Sharma",
