      "spoken": "Madam Speaker, I find it extremely unfortunate that these types of issues are raised on the floor of Council after this morning\u2019s discussion about the morale of our staff, but I\u2019m more than happy to share what many of us already know, is that Councillor\u2026not Councillor, sorry, but maybe he would be a good Councillor\u2026our Acting CAO has made it very clear that he has no intention of applying for the position. As a matter of fact, after the grief and aggravation he\u2019s been through, who knows what he may want to do in the near future. ",
